<body>
    <h1>Technical Document -  Karna</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <hr local-id=3D"b7850bb52806">
<h1 local-id=3D"d21c34345cb6" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-1.Introduction"=
>1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"5f3f3acf2c07" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-1.1Purpose">1.1=
 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"acdd8a874b95">The purpose of this document is to describe th=
e implementation of <strong>HTTPS security on an Nginx web server</strong> =
by configuring <strong>SSL/TLS encryption, HTTP to HTTPS redirection, and b=
asic security headers</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4e30608a1549">This document provides a detailed explanation =
of the configuration process, infrastructure design, security implementatio=
n, and validation steps performed to secure web traffic.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8468c39f455f">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"459f33bc4bd7">
<li local-id=3D"768ed6cbf46c">
<p local-id=3D"04ae2f8659d3"><strong>CTO</strong> =E2=80=93 to understand t=
he infrastructure security architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b63c72294e80">
<p local-id=3D"cc2798ebfdf5"><strong>Solution Architects</strong> =E2=80=93=
 to evaluate the secure web server design</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"52418a9e5e77">
<p local-id=3D"1f8c9555d3ab"><strong>DevOps Engineers</strong> =E2=80=93 to=
 understand implementation and configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db47be02dc17">
<p local-id=3D"d8c28be5a56f"><strong>Developers</strong> =E2=80=93 to under=
stand secure application delivery</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4fcfa52acce">
<p local-id=3D"d851d0ff3c96"><strong>Resellers / Partners</strong> =E2=80=
=93 to understand the deployment architecture</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c4e6dd299121">
<h2 local-id=3D"8a0e4920df59" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-1.2Scope">1.2 S=
cope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ebba00a62201">This document covers the <strong>implementatio=
n of HTTPS security on an Nginx server</strong> deployed on a Linux cloud i=
nstance.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0a9447cf39b1">The scope includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5f8b08adc20e">
<li local-id=3D"9f457b2cf31e">
<p local-id=3D"06dfd34d97ed">Installing and configuring <strong>Nginx web s=
erver</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"883e26cf9bef">
<p local-id=3D"778fa40f6e62">Generating a <strong>self-signed SSL certifica=
te</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21ac4d38c5a0">
<p local-id=3D"570df9b30af0">Configuring <strong>HTTPS communication</stron=
g></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f097d241f392">
<p local-id=3D"a9890bddae06">Implementing <strong>HTTP to HTTPS redirection=
</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b31577d5aee3">
<p local-id=3D"d1f7df6242d6">Adding <strong>basic security headers</strong>=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78149732bae9">
<p local-id=3D"db5defe611fb">Validating the configuration through <strong>b=
rowser and CLI testing</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4cd7baaab426">This implementation demonstrates a <strong>bas=
ic secure web server setup typically used in development and testing enviro=
nments</strong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6ba89c88951b">
<h1 local-id=3D"618e69bc63ca" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-2.OverviewofDev=
OpsProject">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"dcf6822fb2d4" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-2.1Definition">=
2.1 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"64650ed34529">DevOps is a combination of <strong>development=
 and operations practices</strong> that aims to automate infrastructure, im=
prove collaboration, and enable faster and more reliable software delivery.=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"a4961590f0d2">In this implementation, DevOps practices are a=
pplied to configure a <strong>secure web server infrastructure</strong> tha=
t ensures encrypted communication between users and the web server using <s=
trong>SSL/TLS protocols</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9570db8aa45b">Benefits include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e5de3995e40c">
<li local-id=3D"d9cf425e34ee">
<p local-id=3D"cee85f967204">Secure data transmission</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c02f719295d5">
<p local-id=3D"e19721d8a625">Improved reliability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca029ade2a90">
<p local-id=3D"3000d9876459">Faster infrastructure setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5bf98eaf0e7">
<p local-id=3D"557f899a41c3">Standardized server configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"aa7d677b3857">
<h2 local-id=3D"88a0d86b8598" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-2.2KeyPrinciple=
s=E2=80=93AWSWellArchitectedFramework">2.2 Key Principles =E2=80=93 AWS Wel=
l Architected Framework</h2>
<p local-id=3D"767ee55e0b60">This solution follows the <strong>six pillars =
of the AWS Well-Architected Framework</strong>.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"0be5c67b0f9a" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-OperationalExce=
llence">Operational Excellence</h3>
<p local-id=3D"d49231dc0ad5">Infrastructure is configured using structured =
commands and configuration validation such as:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo ng=
inx -t</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"eaa24828fe11">to ensure reliable server configuration.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"3eb46b331fd2" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-Security">Secur=
ity</h3>
<p local-id=3D"bbc71edad9de">Security is implemented through:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd2e70546d6a">
<li local-id=3D"a6dd5d3d2c1e">
<p local-id=3D"a7970266f750">SSL/TLS encryption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"31b0ab2d8936">
<p local-id=3D"d648cf56c1bd">Security headers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c8bf0f32f20">
<p local-id=3D"0745d21841eb">Firewall configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dea8bc3de399">
<p local-id=3D"91c8736348f8">Secure file permissions</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"fc84098e523f" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-Reliability">Re=
liability</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5cadf775d030">Configuration testing ensures Nginx loads succ=
essfully without errors before deployment.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"9d9b790f78c4" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-PerformanceEffi=
ciency">Performance Efficiency</h3>
<p local-id=3D"2f53b3615df5">Nginx is a high-performance web server capable=
 of handling large numbers of concurrent connections.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"43b0d71d78f3" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-CostOptimizatio=
n">Cost Optimization</h3>
<p local-id=3D"906a21aec7ab">The solution uses:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d2415b062175">
<li local-id=3D"8ac9c6ac7fbe">
<p local-id=3D"d6a16d0b56e1">Open-source <strong>Nginx</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"51c92fbcd03e">
<p local-id=3D"d16658d68e8e"><strong>Self-signed SSL certificates</strong><=
/p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2096c46d0abc">which eliminates licensing costs during testin=
g.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"c7f546599fc4" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-Sustainability"=
>Sustainability</h3>
<p local-id=3D"d73e42e899f8">Efficient server configuration ensures minimal=
 resource consumption.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"dd8acf9d7ada">
<h2 local-id=3D"1ec5d6e0bc99" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-2.3GoalsandObje=
ctives">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b59827ea0953">The primary goals of this implementation are:<=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"c23029b96570">
<li local-id=3D"38ceabd514c1">
<p local-id=3D"99f712b7e481">Deploy a <strong>secure Nginx web server</stro=
ng></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4667a67e26a9">
<p local-id=3D"f79b57a7d809">Enable <strong>HTTPS encrypted communication</=
strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"efaf3cb72e00">
<p local-id=3D"10002098185a">Implement <strong>automatic HTTP =E2=86=92 HTT=
PS redirection</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aa899c5255cf">
<p local-id=3D"520f27fbc477">Configure <strong>basic security headers</stro=
ng></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba10023948ac">
<p local-id=3D"c6414d37a0b4">Validate the configuration using <strong>brows=
er and command-line tools</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ecbde843482a">
<h2 local-id=3D"9db917a86a4d" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-2.4Constraintsa=
ndAssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"151f7a11311d" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-Constraints">Co=
nstraints</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"777a660dbd31">
<li local-id=3D"e17b9eb6d102">
<p local-id=3D"8b7522db4546">Self-signed certificate used instead of truste=
d CA certificate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afdec466a872">
<p local-id=3D"ac20211ff4d5">Limited time for implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa07893f6ecc">
<p local-id=3D"f239c0695694">Single-server architecture</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"072cd0b88974" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-Assumptions">As=
sumptions</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"686ceba59251">
<li local-id=3D"14e3c1e43643">
<p local-id=3D"323bf9aabfbc">Server is running <strong>Ubuntu Linux</strong=
></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81c07e3bf289">
<p local-id=3D"8eca10f91b09">Nginx installed via <strong>APT package manage=
r</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6bc9acda30f1">
<p local-id=3D"2a545b19d93f">Firewall configured using <strong>UFW</strong>=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d791d0e759c1">
<p local-id=3D"0509a615d9fd">Public IP is available for browser testing</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"04bdb5f7469b">
<h1 local-id=3D"f0edded6077d" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-3.Architecturea=
ndInfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"c1d18348847b" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-3.1Infrastructu=
reOverview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"65a2b0cdbba4">The infrastructure consists of a <strong>singl=
e Linux cloud server running Nginx with HTTPS enabled</strong>.</p><span cl=
ass=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-emb=
edded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" al=
t=3D"image (13)-20260322-122824.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"=
17c0a3bbb09a7b00a538b5e72dc1a9d99f9de64e73a8310883566d790a927fac" data-imag=
e-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1856045075/=
image%20(13)-20260322-122824.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1774182=
532862&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"776" data-width=3D=
"2304" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"18870=
43878" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"atta=
chment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image (13)-20260322-122824.pn=
g" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource=
-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1856045075=
" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"4" data-media-id=3D"90b7c42a-96=
83-4fac-81a3-58d0c8442b32" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"157"></span>
<p local-id=3D"ee014ec504f2">Components involved:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"20a5c09f4603">
<li local-id=3D"d7bb0c94b005">
<p local-id=3D"4e27448831ce">Linux Server (Ubuntu)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"073855a087f1">
<p local-id=3D"8ed2d1233748">Nginx Web Server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae644ac42a28">
<p local-id=3D"5a5fedebf7a1">SSL/TLS Certificate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5a19602eb9f2">
<p local-id=3D"ce350b30211a">UFW Firewall</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b0ed4a38b6e9">
<p local-id=3D"fa3254cf5016">Internet Client (Browser)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"16d9581b7412">User requests are encrypted using SSL/TLS befo=
re reaching the web server.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"cae0e4948396">
<h2 local-id=3D"29e9b7ec7a7a" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-3.2Environments=
">3.2 Environments</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a723df5803df">For this task, only a <strong>single developme=
nt/testing environment</strong> was used.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"4=
06d1d0d-7a6d-45ea-928a-9d5f6d1d3345" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ba4fbba9921b">
<th data-local-id=3D"e5b88262bd54" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1e6095a8ae60">Environment</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"dcb64d61afb1" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"25726a263c92">Purpose</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"95b89c857f2d">
<td data-local-id=3D"1b88dde1bb0d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cb0894c3aae7">Development</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fc7460c6531a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f6af703c3758">Server configuration and setup</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a65b84d7026d">
<td data-local-id=3D"84862aa4b83b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cfaeec08b3c7">Testing</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2a387cdb3fca" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2f4d8ed12223">Validation of HTTPS and security headers</p></=
td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"eb673bbebe24">Production environments were <strong>not used =
in this implementation</strong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"ec003937e6e6">
<h2 local-id=3D"417e089997fb" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-3.4ApplicationA=
rchitecture&amp;UserRequestFlow">3.4 Application Architecture &amp; User Re=
quest Flow</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"b6dccb507ccc" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-ArchitectureDia=
gram">Architecture Diagram</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">User Br=
owser
     =E2=94=82
     =E2=94=82 HTTPS Request
     =E2=96=BC
Internet
     =E2=94=82
     =E2=96=BC
Linux Server (Cloud Instance)
     =E2=94=82
     =E2=96=BC
Nginx Web Server
     =E2=94=82
     =E2=96=BC
SSL/TLS Encryption
     =E2=94=82
     =E2=96=BC
Website Content</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"27e47d572281">
<h3 local-id=3D"25fe94bb945d" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-SecureUserReque=
stFlow">Secure User Request Flow</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ad0906a95857">
<li local-id=3D"b2b232492a16">
<p local-id=3D"c5e989b5a9fd">User accesses the server using its <strong>pub=
lic IP address</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"658fc0ebc41b">
<p local-id=3D"980c00bc93ea">Browser sends an HTTP request.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c10444c741a">
<p local-id=3D"ab142da70972">Nginx automatically <strong>redirects HTTP req=
uests to HTTPS</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7aafe5fe0322">
<p local-id=3D"521d357c51c3">SSL/TLS handshake establishes encrypted commun=
ication.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc2ab21da1e1">
<p local-id=3D"2c3783715ba3">Nginx serves the requested content securely.</=
p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"2f49e44a4538">
<h2 local-id=3D"2bca3e4e77f0" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-3.3ToolsandTech=
nologies">3.3 Tools and Technologies</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"8=
7abcee3-e047-4a0f-a062-490f07f4f096" class=3D"confluenceTable">
