</div>
<hr local-id=3D"c954dfbd9e03">
<h1 local-id=3D"bc7ae6b5b7a2" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-4.DevelopmentPr=
actices">4. Development Practices</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"541876c70091" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-4.1VersionContr=
ol">4.1 Version Control</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ddbee6274cb4">Not applicable for this implementation.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a60ae8f13775">This task focuses on <strong>server configurat=
ion rather than application code development</strong>, therefore version co=
ntrol systems like Git were not used.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"9312e3df3bb9">
<h2 local-id=3D"ca173a0de6a6" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-4.2ContinuousIn=
tegration">4.2 Continuous Integration</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6241130ff099">Not applicable for this implementation.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4d6fbe80dc44">This project does not include application buil=
ds or automated pipelines.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7fc029912d79">
<h2 local-id=3D"378ea8ddde81" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-4.3AutomatedTes=
ting">4.3 Automated Testing</h2>
<p local-id=3D"759bb7648476">Automated testing was partially implemented us=
ing <strong>command line verification</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8ae24321ecbb">Example:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">curl -I=
 https://&lt;server-ip&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"df1e70a3936e">This verifies the presence of security headers=
.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a053d0f6dcde">
<h2 local-id=3D"6901d8b21f89" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-4.4CodeQualitya=
ndAnalysis">4.4 Code Quality and Analysis</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9a489fa82531">Configuration quality was ensured using:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo ng=
inx -t</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"1ffd59ded7ab">which verifies the correctness of the Nginx co=
nfiguration file before reloading the server.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"3a57dcd9a1d2">
<h1 local-id=3D"db58c1d9762e" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-5.Deploymentand=
ReleaseManagement">5. Deployment and Release Management</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"a6ac15cdbfb6" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-5.1DeploymentSt=
rategy">5.1 Deployment Strategy</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d37df8c42027">A <strong>direct server configuration deployme=
nt strategy</strong> was used.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9acd3a3c832e">Changes were applied to the Nginx configuratio=
n file and immediately tested before reloading the service.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"fca9adcbc4d0">
<h2 local-id=3D"15d48bd85fe6" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-5.2Configuratio=
nManagement">5.2 Configuration Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e218dfa6ea82">Key configuration files used:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">/etc/ng=
inx/sites-available/default</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"682e36184113">SSL certificate storage:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">/etc/ng=
inx/ssl/nginx-selfsigned.crt
/etc/nginx/ssl/nginx-selfsigned.key</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"ca7b17f56cf1">
<h2 local-id=3D"e1c40f7713b5" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-5.3ContinuousDe=
livery/Deployment">5.3 Continuous Delivery / Deployment</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2804f3c1feba">Not applicable for this implementation.</p>
<p local-id=3D"20427a417215">The configuration was performed manually witho=
ut CI/CD automation.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"22affcf4b820">
<h1 local-id=3D"23eb000e015c" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-6.Monitoringand=
IncidentManagement">6. Monitoring and Incident Management</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"1fa3d980b3db" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-6.1MonitoringTo=
olsandMetrics">6.1 Monitoring Tools and Metrics</h2>
<p local-id=3D"1e145388d407">Basic monitoring can include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"603507685f23">
<li local-id=3D"cdf48536e14c">
<p local-id=3D"191c61664570">Nginx server status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6970bf669ee">
<p local-id=3D"da13037644e9">HTTP response codes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4bc2916830a7">
<p local-id=3D"8fdf9ad0b889">SSL certificate validity</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19d5c849b958">
<p local-id=3D"95d879d7c4bd">Server logs</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9caf150d2099">
<h2 local-id=3D"25b90c8e9606" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-6.2AlertingandN=
otification">6.2 Alerting and Notification</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b9034f49d0ed">Not implemented in this task.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0ad8caf8f164">In production environments, alerting systems s=
uch as <strong>Prometheus or CloudWatch</strong> can be configured.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"3dbae7569e7d">
<h2 local-id=3D"38c8975dec01" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-6.3IncidentMana=
gement">6.3 Incident Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"153765fce97d">If server issues occur, the following steps ca=
n be performed:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ffc5d04d85d3">
<li local-id=3D"5286bc46f49b">
<p local-id=3D"581daed3bd42">Check Nginx logs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b01ec6992f9">
<p local-id=3D"5c6e819ebf0f">Validate configuration using <code>nginx -t</c=
ode></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"937d722fcb9b">
<p local-id=3D"aaaffac49119">Restart the Nginx service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f18d1a4c2472">
<p local-id=3D"b08179080ad7">Review firewall configuration</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"c2688af15fd2">
<h1 local-id=3D"867fbedc0c6f" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-7.Security&amp;=
Compliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h1>
<p local-id=3D"a8af819bf450">Security best practices implemented include:</=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"4f2aec195f98">
<li local-id=3D"1ddafe0fcfd1">
<p local-id=3D"a2423afa250e">SSL/TLS encryption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ebb70e90e57">
<p local-id=3D"56d923a7c1a0">HTTP to HTTPS redirection</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"590145b3678b">
<p local-id=3D"1fad0dcbeac8">Secure SSL private key permissions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9825d58e548c">
<p local-id=3D"82d2d6a54f90">Security headers</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"15fcf6231b1d">Configured headers:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">X-Frame=
-Options: SAMEORIGIN
X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"cae959b4b4d1">These protect against:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"62f2fc4f8433">
<li local-id=3D"fcc12facd79a">
<p local-id=3D"c37ee6806f91">Clickjacking attacks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7dd1000dc5a2">
<p local-id=3D"7cd9903ebd1d">MIME type sniffing attacks</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cb515b807499">
<h1 local-id=3D"cf59f600cd02" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-8.CostOptimizat=
ion">8. Cost Optimization</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e535fbc98b75">The solution minimizes cost by using:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"487500b14fd9">
<li local-id=3D"e6a9faec638c">
<p local-id=3D"c339897970cd">Open-source Nginx</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe83a68063fa">
<p local-id=3D"5929b660fa5c">Self-signed certificates</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf42157c827c">
<p local-id=3D"d831c8f66832">Single compute instance</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"fc592bd5c2fa">A detailed <strong>TCO model is not applicable=
 for this small-scale implementation</strong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"606be68ffcce">
<h1 local-id=3D"63a1f6ff907d" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-10.Implementati=
onTimeline">10. Implementation Timeline</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"ae09e2719c30" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-10.1Milestonesa=
