<p local-id=3D"3b2db7ece14e">Duration: 20 minutes</p>
<p local-id=3D"fc6c6248de23">Activities:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0fe4c5591dc6">
<li local-id=3D"6ac11f8cf4b5">
<p local-id=3D"e2d45ad5e1bb">Install Nginx</p></li>
