<hr local-id=3D"4be9fc3c0d38">
<h3 local-id=3D"3aa417916aa5" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-Phase5=E2=80=93=
BrowserHTTPSValidation">Phase 5 =E2=80=93 Browser HTTPS Validation</h3>
<p local-id=3D"9915f806711a">Duration: 10 minutes</p>
