Retrospectives">11.1 Feedback and Retrospectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8dfc1a85437c">Feedback from DevOps engineers and security te=
ams can help improve server security configurations.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"ab2c0cde7016">
<h2 local-id=3D"e825da3dd89c" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-11.2IterativeEn=
hancements">11.2 Iterative Enhancements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ec14ea93a538">Future improvements may include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e6e605d0b99b">
<li local-id=3D"0f170f24f9dc">
<p local-id=3D"d7d129ed2705">Using <strong>Let's Encrypt certificates</stro=
ng></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94a8efd0dc93">
<p local-id=3D"ccf39c9bef29">Implementing <strong>automatic SSL renewal</st=
rong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"33ffe97475f5">
<p local-id=3D"61b14eb27fae">Adding <strong>Web Application Firewall</stron=
g></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb72d81fcfb9">
<p local-id=3D"eaff8a5471e3">Integrating <strong>monitoring and alerting sy=
stems</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7771796f6a73">
<h1 local-id=3D"60d4e096f75d" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-12.Conclusion">=
12. Conclusion</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"5cd2a7bd8b8f" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-12.1Summary">12=
.1 Summary</h2>
<p local-id=3D"954c516b2d0d">This project successfully implemented a <stron=
g>secure Nginx web server using HTTPS encryption</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"199b1d3d6976">Key achievements include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"370cbb854fe7">
<li local-id=3D"1031dd1ad36f">
<p local-id=3D"0f2b72044aa4">HTTPS enabled using SSL/TLS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"da2bf484ab1e">
<p local-id=3D"7cf5590f4e95">Automatic HTTP =E2=86=92 HTTPS redirection</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"9365aabec513">
<p local-id=3D"d730b08fb8a2">Security headers configured</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e39b67e629f2">
<p local-id=3D"629f5d384052">Firewall rules implemented</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb7fd8cdb871">
<p local-id=3D"44c5474fedb6">Configuration validated successfully</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"12826cf40d51">The implementation ensures <strong>secure comm=
unication between users and the server</strong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"1c1ec4b1eac5">
<h2 local-id=3D"7878de5acd78" id=3D"TechnicalDocument-Karna-12.2NextSteps">=
12.2 Next Steps</h2>
